          <h1><span>THE</span> PRESENT</h1>
          <p>Taking inspiration from the initial Magpul concept, Ronin staff went to the drawing board and re-designed every facet of the motorcycle from scratch, creating the high-performance Ronin you see today in a limited run of 47 total motorcycles.  With Magpul approval that the final version stayed true to the initial concept in form and spirit despite being transformed functionally into a different motorcycle entirely, the final version of the “Magpul Ronin” was completed late in 2012. </p>
      </div>
